fields.name: Prosthetic Leg
fields.detail: Help someone take their next step towards independence and mobility by donating a prosthetic leg. Your contribution provides not just a limb, but a renewed sense of freedom and possibility. Every donation makes a real difference in someone's life.

fields.name: Walking Stick
fields.detail: Donate a walking stick to support individuals with mobility challenges. Your contribution provides essential stability and independence, helping them move with confidence and ease. Every donation makes a meaningful impact.

fields.name: Wheelchairs
fields.detail: Your donation of a wheelchair can give someone the gift of mobility and independence. Help improve their quality of life by supporting those in need of essential mobility aids. Every contribution makes a difference!
